        <h1>標誌設計 Logo Design</h1>
        <p>數位發展部標誌以「群眾・訊號・連結」的意涵出發，強調部門任務不僅關注數位技術發展，更擔任了資源媒合之角色，其中橫跨了經濟產業、資通安全、城鄉發展等領域。</p>
        <p>The logo of the Ministry of Digital Affairs (moda) incorporates the core ideas of “people,” “signal,” and “connectivity.” It spotlights moda’s focus on digital technology development as well as its role matching resources in key fields such as the economy, industry, cyber security, and regional development.</p>
      </div>
