            {% for slide in slides %}
            <li class="glide__slide">
              <img src="{{ slide }}" alt="">
            </li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p>從硬體平台到數位雲端，從開發端的編寫序列，再單元擴散至人民參與，標誌造型由幾何化的 I/O 線段所共構，透過具方向性的符號組成隱喻，詮釋部門實踐 Crowd to Cloud to Crowd 之系列進程；透過多領域合作，橋接數位民主。</p>
        <p>The logo, composed of geometric I/O lines, spans hardware, platforms, to cloud technology, from developer coding to civic participation. Its directional symbols are a metaphor illustrating moda’s “Crowd to Cloud to Crowd” methodology connecting digital democracy through interdisciplinary collaborations.</p>
        <a href="{{ pdf.url }}">Download pdf 💾</a>
